  <datafield tag="245" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">Sine-Gordon model coupled with a free scalar field emergent in the low-energy phase dynamics of a mixture of pseudospin-1/2 Bose gases with interspecies spin exchange</subfield>
